snippet.title: Introducing The Shills - Join Us For A Banter
snippet.description: So The Shills are a group of globe defenders who like to gather and, well, take apart all the nonsense the flerfs put out, and these guys (and gals) do it in such a funny and unique way, it is really entertaining. So, to showcase them off a little bit more, you get a 2 hour livestream with me, taking questions from everyone in the chat and basically just having a good time. https://www.youtube.com/c/TheShills
